name: Datepicker
body:
#Date Picker
###Lightweight javascript framework-free datepicker

Based on [DtTvB work](http://javascriptkit.com/script/script2/dyndateselector.shtml), this date picker is just an improved way for automatic use on for fields.
It also includes some bugfixes, improvements and fully compatible with IE8+.

No third-party library dependency.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
